      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone seeking dependable transportation without the premium price of a showroom-ready car. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few minor door dings, and some thinning of the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. Mechanically, the car starts up reliably and handles well, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future to restore its original ride quality. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that\u2019s ready to be driven daily as-is.",
